trans-unit.source: Provides an editor in a design host such as [!INCLUDE[vsprvslong](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] to edit the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WizardStepCollection"></xref> object of a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizard"></xref> Web server control.
Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.CreateUserWizardStepCollectionEditor"></xref> class using the given <xref:System.Type>.
The <xref:System.Type> of the items in the collection associated with the collection editor.
Returns a value indicating whether a provided object can be removed from the collection.
A <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WizardStep"></xref> object to determine whether it can be removed from the collection.

<xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WizardStep"></xref> can be removed from the collection; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
Creates a modal dialog box for editing the contents of a collection of <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizardStep"></xref> objects.

Gets the <xref uid="langword_csharp_Help" name="Help" href=""></xref> keyword used to display the Help topic or topic list when users click the **Help** button or press the F1 key in the editor's dialog box.
The <xref uid="langword_csharp_Help" name="Help" href=""></xref> keyword to display the Help topic or topic list when Help is requested from the editor.
